  "body": "1.  Move all files to FHS locations.  In particular, the credentials directory needs to get out of `/etc`.  `/var/lib/condor` is fine -- as well as `/var/cache/scitokens-credmon`.\r\n2.  Have `example.conf` (or similar) get dropped into the `config.d` directory.\r\n3.  Binaries that aren't expected to be executed directly by users (such as the `SEC_CREDENTIAL_PRODUCER`) should go into `/usr/libexec`, not `/usr/bin`.", 
